<!doctype html>
<html>

<head>
    <% include includes/head.ejs %>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <% include includes/header.ejs %>
    </header>
    <div class="submit-form-container">
        <div class="col-12">
            <form action="" method="POST">

                <br>
                <br> Please select the activity you participated in today:
                <br>
               
                <% for(var i=0; i < activities.length; i++) { %>
                    <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="activitylist" value="<%= activities[i].activity %>" /><%= activities[i].activity %> 
                    </label>
                    <% } %>

                <br>
                <h3>Pre-session:</h3>
                <p>
                    <i>This section refers to how you were feeling before
                        <span class="activity">activity</span>.</i>
                </p>
                <br>
                <br> Today, I felt:
                <br>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="presession" value="great" />Great
                </label>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="presession" value="good" />Good
                </label>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="presession" value="ok" />OK
                </label>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="presession" value="ill" />Ill
                </label>
                <br>
                <br> Overall, I feel that my health is:
                <br>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="health" value="very good" />Very good
                </label>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="health" value="good" />Good
                </label>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="health" value="bad" />Bad
                </label>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="health" value="very bad" />Very bad
                </label>
                <br>
                <br>
                <h3>Post-session:</h3>
                <p>
                    <i>This section refers to how you felt after
                        <span class="activity">activity</span>.</i>
                </p>
                <br> The
                <b>BEST</b> part of
                <span class="activity">activity</span> was:
                <br>
                <input type="text" name="bestpart">
                <br>
                <br> The
                <b>WORST</b> part of
                <span class="activity">activity</span> was:
                <br>
                <input type="text" name="worstpart">
                <br>
                <br> After participating in
                <span class="activity">activity</span>, I would do
                <span class="activity">activity</span> on my own.
                <br>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="postsession" value="strongly agree" />Strongly Agree
                </label>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="postsession" value="agree" />Agree
                </label>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="postsession" value="disagree" />Disagree
                </label>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="postsession" value="strongly disagree" />Strongly Disagree
                </label>
                <br>
                <br>
                <input type="submit" class="submit-visit" value="Submit">
                <br>
                <br>
                <h3>Thank you for completing the Passport to Lifetime Fitness!</h3>
                <br>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <% include includes/footer.ejs %>
    </footer>
</body>